      "weather": "Overcast",
      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SOUTHLINE (1) drew a squeeze box and was game in defeat when a close third, 1.5 lengths from the winner STOMP ROCKER (17.12) at this track. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Can find winning form. BIG DIESEL (6) was a little disappointing last start at Gawler when 4th (31.36) over 531m. Has won here at this journey. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Should be in this for a long way. STOMP ROCKER (4) jumped from box 5 last time and ran away with an impressive win scoring by 4.5 lengths at this track in a handy 22.36. Will need some luck early after drawing a tricky box here. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. In sparkling form and looks the one to beat again. TOLEDO (8) is on a run of two wins – hard to fault that form.",
